high_descs: Turn right and walk to the outside of the counter.
Turn right and walk ahead to the fridge.
Place the apple in the fridge to the left of the lettuce. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and veer right to the microwave.
Place the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple in a microwave.

high_descs: Move to the white counter in the middle of the room with an apple on it.
Pick up the apple that is close to the knife.
Move across the room to fridge.
Place the apple inside the fridge to cool.  Remove apple and close the fridge door.
Turn left and move to the microwave.
Place the apple inside the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Cool an apple to be placed inside the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the apple on the counter, next to the knife.
Turn right, go forward, turn left, go forward, then turn right and go to the fridge.
Turn around, go toward the coffee maker, then turn right and go to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple in the microwave.
